beer.beer_description:
Something this dank, clear and bitter makes us feel like we’re hiking withthumbs in our backpack straps getting lungs full of clean air while being showered by the smells of pine trees, warm earth and a fresh spring bloom.
The bouquet of Mosaic, Enigma and Idaho 7 hops, a supporting malt-derived sweetness and a stiff but refreshing bitterness.
